{"tid":1551562,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[願死者安息] 唱聖詩念經悼念","createTime":"2019-09-08T05:12:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T06:39:12.000Z","uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"46d1ea4ec710885d6b0f6e7122b28c15c72d03cb","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:12:22.000Z","msg":"P牌出post 希望大家諗一諗<br />\n知道大家好嬲 好想搵出真相<br />\n但晚晚無目的去圍黨鐵 拆閘 圍狗屋 放火做路障<br />\n會令活動失焦 同時令我地形象愈黎愈差<br />\n你實話我係和理非<br />\n但宜家叫一句黑警已經俾人拉<br />\n繼續落去只會令我地失去更多手足<br />\n<br />\n我地曾經有二萬人一齊上街<br />\n宜家唔止要令呢二百萬人團結<br />\n更加要感化其他果五百萬人<br />\n<br />\n<strong>悼念死者</strong><br />\n手足犧牲 我地每個人都好傷心<br />\n近日仲有大量人自殺<br />\n我地更加要為死者唱聖詩、念經<br />\n為亡靈祈求安息主懷，享天鄉永福<br />\n主自會為我地打開天堂嘅門<br />\n<br />\n願主與你們同在<br />\nSing Hallelujah to the Lord<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他宗教信仰同樣歡迎"},{"pid":"cddd80592a628e9225f48bb7e846b285cff3a828","tid":1551562,"uid":7971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"今日<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱fuck the popo <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱毅進仔<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔係</span>唱今天我 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">今日係唱The Star-Spangled Banner</span>🇺🇸🇺🇸<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>一定一定要係國際媒體面前一齊全民大合唱啊<br />\n點都要唱到第一段啊！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<del>因為全首太長</del><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\nOh, say can you see by the dawn's early light<br />\nWhat so proudly we hailed at the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\nWhose broad stripes and bright stars thru the perilous fight,<br />\nO'er the ramparts we watched were so gallantly streaming?<br />\nAnd the rocket's red glare, the bombs bursting in air,<br />\nGave proof through the night that our flag was still there.<br />\nOh, say does that star-spangled banner yet wave<br />\nO'er the land of the free and the home of the brave?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">背熟第一段</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">叫英文口號</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong>五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Five demands Not one less</span><br />\n香港警察 知法犯法<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Hong Kong Police breaking the peace</span><br />\n與港同在 促成人權法案<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Stand with Hong Kong, pass the democracy act</span><br />\n為自由抗爭 制度已失衡<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Fight for freedom, no faith in the systems</span> </strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">應對記者資料</span></span><br />\n<br />\n[置頂][行動] 9月8點應對外國記者+3首歌歌詞+資料整合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1551469\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1551469</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"7935f181ffb334e7a6c4078a916197334efd3d82","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:35:26.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 照十連 宗教自由"},{"pid":"da1dbd1710e9528f64a776484aee0686a329d7b3","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:35:50.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 照十連 耶撚召喚"},{"pid":"5f65058fa02fccf3f9fe040d2dc631068c71a384","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:36:04.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 照十連 聖詩"},{"pid":"d35d3cc0d3170e2dd288d24120121845d13c0d6b","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:36:17.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 照十連 念經"},{"pid":"392bb1edae7fc105a564f5161d4208232aeccc1d","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:36:35.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 照十連 超渡"},{"pid":"6445b7a1e81588e77085e3699a10f7f8e627e0a2","tid":1551562,"uid":258851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T06:37:18.000Z","msg":"推唔到post 照十連 悼念"},{"pid":"bfe66dce803dded67b2f66b37bc7a43445274806","t